We come together
to celebrate Kate and Philip...

28:17.529 --> 28:19.065
KATE:
Admit it.

28:19.198 --> 28:21.467
You hated me
the first time we met.

28:22.634 --> 28:25.537
And maybe I hated you
a little bit, too.

28:25.637 --> 28:28.207
So, no, this was not
a "love at first sight"

28:28.307 --> 28:30.476
magical fairytale romance.

28:30.576 --> 28:32.411
It was gritty.

28:32.544 --> 28:34.480
-Flaws up front.
-Mm-hmm.

28:36.248 --> 28:39.385
A Super Bowl ring only worthy

28:39.485 --> 28:41.220
