(laughter)

28:47.593 --> 28:49.728
I give you this ring

28:49.829 --> 28:51.898
as a sign of my love.

28:52.899 --> 28:56.235
KATE:
And I give you this ring
as a sign of my love.

28:57.403 --> 28:59.638
OFFICIANT:
And there you have it.
