just seems to come at us.

31:22.381 --> 31:24.450
All of us.

31:24.550 --> 31:27.653
You know, the years
just keep flying by,

31:27.753 --> 31:30.622
faster and faster.

31:32.158 --> 31:35.394
It can give a guy whiplash,
just thinking about it.

31:39.498 --> 31:42.068
And so while I would love
nothing more than to...

31:42.168 --> 31:45.237
