to build a remote

31:50.876 --> 31:53.512
that pauses life.

31:53.612 --> 31:56.082
-Damn.
-(laughter)

31:56.182 --> 31:58.284
That doesn't mean
there aren't still

31:58.384 --> 32:01.487
summer vacations to be enjoyed.

32:01.587 --> 32:04.823
Still good conversations
to be had.

32:04.923 --> 32:07.459
And still love to be shared.

32:09.128 --> 32:12.531
It just all happens much faster.

32:13.865 --> 32:16.168
But, um...

32:16.268 --> 32:18.204
in moments like this,

32:18.304 --> 32:20.872
when you're around
all your favorite people...

32:21.873 --> 32:25.444
...celebrating
a really special day...

32:26.512 --> 32:29.048
...time does slow down
ever so much.

32:30.816 --> 32:32.851
So I'm grateful to Kate

32:32.951 --> 32:35.187
and Philip for that.

32:38.490 --> 32:41.860
And I'm filled with comfort,
as I look around this room,

32:41.960 --> 32:44.363
knowing that all of you
will be on this

32:44.463 --> 32:46.999
speeding train with me,

32:47.099 --> 32:50.036
slowing down
for the occasional special stop.

32:50.169 --> 32:53.872
All the way till the very end.

32:53.972 --> 32:56.642
So, um...

32:56.742 --> 32:58.210
cheers.

32:58.310 --> 33:00.879
-MAN: Cheers.
-WOMAN: Cheers.

33:01.013 --> 33:03.382
(smacks lips)

33:03.515 --> 33:05.384
Okay.

33:05.484 --> 33:07.853
And now to drag us
back from the dark abyss

33:07.986 --> 33:09.688
that I just pushed us all into.

33:09.821 --> 33:12.524
(laughter)

33:12.658 --> 33:14.160
Uh, it is my pleasure
to introduce

33:14.260 --> 33:16.562
a very special performance.

33:16.695 --> 33:19.365
So without further ado,
ladies and gentlemen, I give you

33:19.498 --> 33:21.867
the one, the only...

33:21.967 --> 33:24.203
Mom.

33:31.277 --> 33:33.212
The stage is all yours, Mom.

33:37.049 --> 33:39.385
(whispering indistinctly)

33:58.570 --> 34:00.772
It took me a sec,
