34:29.701 --> 34:32.104
-Mm-hmm.
-Yeah.

34:38.444 --> 34:40.512
You know something
that Pound of Ham Rebecca

34:40.612 --> 34:42.414
-would never do?
-Hmm?

34:42.514 --> 34:45.117
Strut over to that piano over
there and rip it a new one.

34:47.119 --> 34:49.020
(laughs)

34:50.021 --> 34:51.323
Well...

34:51.423 --> 34:53.792
Pound of Ham Rebecca's dead.

34:53.892 --> 34:56.595
Oh, okay.

34:56.695 --> 34:58.797
(laughs)

